{"tid":1497232,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港上《時代雜誌》美國版專訪","createTime":"2019-08-23T01:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T06:34:41.000Z","uid":296674,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4d7aed9eb8ae130251e8de7e2f6c2fcd1322590d","tid":1497232,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:19:20.000Z","msg":"又係我銀叉巴<br />\n<br />\n話說我校有訂閱 TIME magazine，宿舍大堂任睇<br />\n<br />\n點知我唔小心一揭，見到一版版雨傘、黑衣人、催淚彈；主題喺《為香港的靈魂而戰》<br />\n<br />\n嘩，我真係覺得香港人好犀利，我覺得非常自豪<br />\n<br />\n大家繼續努力，五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\nBe water, be humble<br />\n全世界都支持你哋"},{"pid":"da62b1e674defe8ea1476949d28b8e121846da25","tid":1497232,"uid":296674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:26:02.000Z","msg":"補圖<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Do3goDd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDo3goDd.jpg&h=c94307a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7e1hSwA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7e1hSwA.jpg&h=ce346fd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k9QOeKW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk9QOeKW.jpg&h=c033b4a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9sdoN4X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9sdoN4X.jpg&h=ca156451&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a116a7626e81d8f8059899772803d0ca8eefabb","tid":1497232,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:26:19.000Z","msg":"大家要做得好好睇睇"},{"pid":"7cc75f9c3f5c649b4a878818495294adfbea8cce","tid":1497232,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:26:42.000Z","msg":"全世界嘅目光都係香港度"},{"pid":"f89f760e227d6b4e3a683a7fcfeb1655494d5881","tid":1497232,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:28:07.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推"},{"pid":"c99c67bd8abc609b52a365f93429684257a41995","tid":1497232,"uid":18910